summary: This appears to be a chain of custody form for intercepted evidence (ELSUR - Electronic Surveillance) related to an FBI case. It documents the transfer of evidence for permanent storage, indicating it contains intercepted material, possibly from a Title III court-authorized intercept or consensual monitoring.
